Now to create Visualization for the index pattern which you have created.
•	Now click on 3 dot
•	Now click on visualize
•	Now we are not selecting any pre-defined visualizations
•	So we are clicking create visualizations
•	Select pie chart
•	And now select the filebeat which your have selected earlier
•	Now you can change the visualization
•	In the right side click on options
•	Uncheck the donut
•	Show labels and click on update
•	Now click on save and give the name and click on save

Now to create dashboard for the index pattern which you have created
•	Now click on 3 dot
•	Now click on dashboard
•	Now in the top click on dashboard so it will take you to dashboard create page
•	Click on create dashboard
•	Now click on create new in the add an existing or new dashboard
•	Now cl	ick on add an existing
•	Now select the visualization which you have created above
•	Now click on save the dashboard
•	Give the name and click on save.

Now to download default dashboard in the elastic
•	Open the terminal
•	Type sudo filebeat setup -e
•	Now come to elastic
•	Click on 3dot and select dashboard
•	It will show list of dashboard related to filebeat.
•	Now search system
•	And select any one of system dashboard
•	It will display all the details with dashboard.
